<p class="graf graf--p">We are really thankful to the speaker and the audience for helping us make this possible. Also a special thanks to folks at <a class="markup--user markup--p-user" href="https://medium.com/u/738947055a43" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-href="https://medium.com/u/738947055a43" data-anchor-type="2" data-user-id="738947055a43" data-action-value="738947055a43" data-action="show-user-card" data-action-type="hover">DocuSign</a> for providing us with an amazing venue with beautiful scenes.</p>

